	<h1 class="title">马斯克的高速列车还没太多谱，但中国中车已经去谈合作了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/244919/small/244919.jpg?1451146107" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">李硕明 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-29 11:51:23 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/21479/medium/21479.jpg?1454008888" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="21479" data-title="《马斯克的高速列车还没太多谱，但中国中车已经去谈合作了》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/21479/medium/21479.jpg?1454008888" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/21479.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
